            <div class="comment">
                <span class="datetime">13 Mar, 2010</span>

                <p>Mine looked nothing like the photo above.  The flavor was great, but I took them out after 15 minutes and I thnk even that was a bit too long. Mine didn&#039;t flaten, so I think I&#039;ll do that with a spatula next time before I put them in the over.   Good cookie, but needs some adjustments.</p>
            </div>
